The FCC manual seems to indicate this device is running ''Linux'' :(and using U-Boot and busybox, among other things).
Per a device label, a 00:09:37 OUI is used <small>(.. for at least :the Ethernet IF, but it's assumed assumed to be used for both)</small>. :10 or 10/100 Mbit ??
